Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,花火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,花火 你起床了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我去買點東西回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 朋友回去之後就一直在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,絲毫不感興趣的人對自己抱有愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還有比這更讓人噁心的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我說了這麼噁心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,原來一個人的戀愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是如此沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真...倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,難得的週末
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,無視?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼一定要選麥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人就不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要搶走他啊 我只剩下麥了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,麥不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦喜歡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就感覺非那個人不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,兩邊都想要 都不想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真要那樣做的話 兩邊肯定都跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,最後就會變成孤身一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己才是一直在逃避...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那時 我大概還不知戀愛為何物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一年級男生好純真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欲求不滿?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿~不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是中學的學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好誘惑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是早川前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,明明很苗條卻是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,中性打扮 卻有一種難以形容的色情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 你沒興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有啦有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,苗條加巨乳？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼結巴?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐的身體是快要折掉一般的纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部卻很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我只記得那白似透明的肌膚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐非常害怕寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,近乎病態一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐的身體冷颼颼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,明明似夢似幻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可她的熱情卻向我席捲而來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,很害怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼有精神幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你...怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我按了門鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且沒上鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛才還在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怪熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,屋子裡空調開得很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 時機太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,麥 好像有什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別看啊 別看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,支起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,別一副好奇寶寶的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 高中?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不去喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.75,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你還真是與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這叫反社會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,粟屋你倒是學習很拿手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.67,0:12:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,考試加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼了 別哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡那個家教老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,結果到最後誰都不知道我們的關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 讓你當我思春期的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密可以救贖心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看似愜意的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,其實卻無法一笑而過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,果...果然還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對...會控制不住自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,無所謂...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不用控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我還真是沒長進呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我 只是思春期的玩具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想掰斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛那樣很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我又不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這...這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 怎麼說呢
